# (~500MB+ each, 100 bootstrap files per network — all regenerable via
# luminal_her2_pre_networks.R + run_aracne_ap_luminal_her2.sh +
# luminal_her2_mra_kbhb.R). Consolidated networks
# (data/{tcga,mtbrc}_{LumA,LumB,Her2}_network.txt) and the final comparison
